---
title: Caramelized Onion & Swiss Turkey Burgers with Roasted Garlic Horseradish Aioli & Potato Wedges
description: Looking to up your burger game? This version will blow your mind. The spiced beef patties are seared until browned, topped with melty Swiss cheese and buttery caramelized onion, and stuffed into toasted potato buns. Of course, no burger would be complete without a decadent sauce—this one combines mayo, roasted garlic, and wasabi paste (aka horseradish) to create a punchy spread. Pro tip: The aioli also goes great with the crispy potato wedges on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61c232c0bf7b23299c540649-d7711b02.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/caramelized-onion-swiss-turkey-burgers-61c232c0bf7b23299c540649-3c6cbccd.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 1020 kcal
  fat: 60 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
  carbohydrates: 84 g
  sugar: 12 g
  protein: 42 g
  fiber: 7 g
